channel.title: [317] [PI] TwistedPK Release
channel.description:
[center] [url=http://www.upload.ee/image/3522258/banner2.png][img]http://www.upload.ee/thumb/3522258/banner2.png[/img][/url][url=http://www.upload.ee/image/3522258/banner2.png][img]http://www.upload.ee/thumb/3522258/banner2.png[/img][/url] [b][font=arial black][size=2em]TwistedPK[/size][/font][/b] Yo guys, I started coding again and I thought I should contribute with something, so I decided to release this server. After a few days of work, this is what i made, I hope you will enjoy. I know you probably dont know me, but Im active on Rune-Server. Virusscan is included so Dont worry. [b][size=2em]Features:[/size][/b] -Amazing PvM -Fantasic Eco -All skills working except for summoning, just need to add some ClickingButtons. -Working torva,pernix,virtus health -Great PvP , working turmoil and soulsplit, this doesnt have the right gfx for soulsplit though.. -Donator shop, didnt give them to much benefits, there is a dzone but theres nothing in there. -Pk point system -Pk points shop -Godwars maps, working killcount, working bosses. -Good bosses -Minigames are here, but the same for skilling, need to add some Clickingbuttons ect. -634 items -Maps working all over the world, no black marks or anything -Dicing -Report Abusing , fully working -Mboxes, amazing rewards -Voting implemented, need to change to your details, or just remove it for the mysql errors -Vote point shop -Working Jad, one wave though . Easy to add more. -Randomevent command, spawns randoms on certain places -Barrows sets, use chisel to open -Much more, download to check it out!
Home [img]http://www.upload.ee/image/3522288/0bf73153788056f964c5ab8afa8e342c.png[/img] Pk points system [img]http://www.upload.ee/image/3522290/19ce0f8882861854b22f1fc20b15c8ae.png[/img] Donator shop [img]http://www.upload.ee/image/3522292/36d417114e588f7d684638c8a5e2e9f6.png[/img] Skilling [img]http://www.upload.ee/image/3522294/367d4908ef20b5e993674a6ce395e66d.png[/img] Pk point shop [img]http://www.upload.ee/image/3522297/430b6b868c225f64a22b98124fa9d88b.png[/img] PvM [img]http://www.upload.ee/image/3522302/671d02497e84b6127c8b87ac0a29317d.png[/img] Report Abuse, fully working [img]http://www.upload.ee/image/3522344/6819402f707f51d9ea44640214fc9fdb.png[/img] [img]http://www.upload.ee/image/3522349/a2b4db365532d33f89283a4886d9de0e.png[/img] [img]http://www.upload.ee/image/3522351/f613d32e22993c6a687e8c856a3fe58c.png[/img] Godwars Maps [img]http://www.upload.ee/image/3522353/fc4a2fccc0abbbd03bd3a186611c2b8a.png[/img] [img]http://www.upload.ee/image/3522383/f3667acfe50f0de383be73828a14aa1e.png[/img] Dicing [img]http://www.upload.ee/image/3522397/9a5ae1d2f4e40d5ffd8b87f3344eb6f7.png[/img] Slayer [img]http://www.upload.ee/image/3522398/838e486828058aa229ccc3d9a1248841.png[/img]
[b]Building:[/b] The project must be built through Eclipse. The .project and .classpath files still remain, so it shouldn't be too difficult.
Download Link :[url=https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/38155826/TwistedPK.rar]Package[/url]
[b]Credits:[/b] -Insanity, for project insanity -Zak wins, the owner of the base I used -Vincent, a friend of mine who thinks about new content -Pascal, a friend of mine who always helps me with my servers. -Ardi Rizal, last but certainly not least, he always helps me with dupes, errors or anything Im asking him. Respect for this guy.
Some problems I'm aware of u will have to fix, some shouldnt be that hard. -Health orb, not that hard. -Trading is duped as fk, good luck with this. -Duel arena has some dupes, help/snippet is full of spoonfeeds, so not that hard aswell. -The clickingbuttons from things like castle wars ect, cba adding them myself.
Anyways, if you are able to fix everything, you could make a pretty nice server out of this because adding content here isnt hard. If you download this, I wish you the best of luck on your progress [b][i]-Gijs. aka Balkie1000[/i][/b]
VIRUSSCAN: [url=http://onlinelinkscan.com/results/httpsdl-dropboxusercontent-comu38155826twistedpk-rar/]Click[/url][/center]
EDIT: For the hp orb fix: Client sided: go into client.java Search for public void drawHP() { You will see this line: int health = (int)(((double)currentHP / (double)maxHP)); Change it to this: int health = (int)(((double)currentHP / (double)maxHP *100D));
